PrecisRegulations Amending the MANITOBA FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1987 by clarifying the difference between catching and possessing fish, adjusting the fillet length comversion number for walleye and sauger, raising catch limits on trout and artic char caught in "stocked" waters and by adding nine lakes to the list of High Quality Management Waters.
